# Demo: Basic Chat Interaction
# Shows a simple conversation with streaming response

Output docs/images/demo-chat.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms
Set Padding 20

Type "jdai --new"
Enter
Sleep 5s

Type "What is the Fibonacci sequence? Give me a brief explanation and a C# implementation."
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 15s

Screenshot docs/images/demo-chat.png
Sleep 2s
